content.texts: On-demand subscriptions help you maximize cost savings while giving you access to enterprise-grade support.

features.title: Can cancel the subscription any time
Do I still need to pay for technical support with the paid version?

description.description: You can get most of free support

features.title: I do not want to use it, can I unsubscribe?

description.description: Pay-as-you-go can unsubscribe at any time, and the annual subscription is negotiated and unsubscribed according to the actual situation.

features.title: How to get manual support for the free version?

description.description:
虽然我们不针对免费版用户提供免费的人工支持服务，但是您可以作出行动判断：

- 如何您认为是产品故障，请向我们的 GitHub 项目中提交 Issue
- 如果您需要的是个性化服务，请到我们网站的服务页面中购买合适的服务

features.title: Can I use Websoft9 on my Server which have not Internet?

description.description: We can provide offline installation packages for server environments without network. If you have this need, please contact our Customer Success team first

features.title: Can I use Websoft9 on my Private Cloud?

description.description: We can provide service for you, you should contact us before

features.title: I don't want to manage the server, do you offer hosting?

description.description: We can provide you with server hosting services

features.title: Do you provide invoice and contract?
Which public cloud platforms can I subscribe to Websoft9's products?

description.description: 我们在 Azure, AWS, 阿里云，华为云，腾讯云等全球主流的云平台发布了可以[订阅](https://support.websoft9.com/docs/buy/subscription)的商品

content.texts: 立即部署 Websoft9 应用商店，体验软件即服务带来的便利吧
